A shabby apartment in Silverlake.
The TV is on.
NEWSCASTER ...
NEWSCASTER Strangely enough, scientific records do support the fact that we are heading for the biggest solar climax in recorded history...
A small tremor rocks the apartment and the dishevelled face of JACKSON CURTIS, 33, pops up from behind the couch.
He fell asleep at his laptop last night.
JACKSON Oh no.
JACKSON Not again.
